# Setting up Azure storage static website for Jekyll
This is the introductory page and the start of the blog
-->
<div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert"><i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle"></i> <b>Warning:</b> The process described herein is intended for demonstrative purposes only to highlight Azureâ€™s capabilities. You are encouraged not to use an Azure account linked to a company you do not own, and so instructions for creating a new Azure account for personal use are included. The configuration of the security settings of storage accounts linked to your organization needs to be based on your organizationâ€™s security requirements.</div>

<!-- Move this to separate intro section
## Prerequisites:
 - Google Chrome 
